      <title>JAVA环境配置</title>
      <link href="/post/45619.html"/>
      <url>/post/45619.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="JAVA环境配置"><a href="#JAVA环境配置" class="headerlink" title="JAVA环境配置"></a>JAVA环境配置</h1><h2 id="一、首先安装jdk"><a href="#一、首先安装jdk" class="headerlink" title="一、首先安装jdk"></a>一、首先安装jdk</h2><p><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1e73a8271.png" alt="image-20221013220421804"></p><ul><li>首先选择更改：</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1eab9517b.png" alt="image-20221013221114131" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>更换位置，选择除c盘以外的其他盘，本人选择E:\Java\jdk1.8.0_131\，然后点确定</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1ed10bca7.png" alt="image-20221013221337726" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>然后选择开发工具，点下一步：</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1ee6a6d54.png" alt="image-20221013221532672" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>然后等待一会，会出来此界面，点击更改：</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1f114f4af.png" alt="image-20221013221758549" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>选择刚刚E:\Java这个文件夹，在此文件夹下建一个新文件夹，命名为jre1.8.0_131,点击下一步：</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1f2651896.png" alt="image-20221013222203906" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>等待一会，java就安装完毕了，点击关闭即可</li></ul><h2 id="二、配置环境变量"><a href="#二、配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="二、配置环境变量"></a>二、配置环境变量</h2><ul><li>首先找到安装jdk的安装路径，复制jdk的安装路径</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1f5ddc3e1.png" alt="image-20221013223647346" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>点击此电脑右键，选择属性</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1f7b1bdda.png" alt="image-20221013222758753" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>点击高级系统设置</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1f8e7d86a.png" alt="image-20221013223057700" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>点击环境变量</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1fa9ba652.png" alt="image-20221013223205491" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>在系统变量这，选择新建：</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1fc0509dc.png" alt="image-20221013223344915" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>填写变量名为：JAVA_HOME,变量值为jdk的安装路径，我的为E:\java\jdk1.8.0_131</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1fd753651.png" alt="image-20221013224101201" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>然后点击确定，在系统变量中找到Path路径，点击编辑：</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b1ff2af49d.png" alt="image-20221013224322320" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>点击新建，将下图两个路径添加进去：<ul><li>%JAVA_HOME%\bin</li><li>%JAVA_HOME%\jre\bin</li></ul></li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b200c3cc2b.png" alt="image-20221013224801059" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>然后一路点击确定，即将环境变量配置完毕</li></ul><h2 id="三、测试能否编译和运行"><a href="#三、测试能否编译和运行" class="headerlink" title="三、测试能否编译和运行"></a>三、测试能否编译和运行</h2><ul><li>在桌面上建一个文件夹，在里面建一个文本文件，文本文件命名为HelloWord.java,注意后缀名为java</li><li>点开文件将此段代码复制，然后保存：</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">HelloWord</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>点开刚刚建的文件夹，在红框内输入cmd,然后回车：</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b2023c49e7.png" alt="image-20221013225445799" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>然后在cmd窗口内输入javac HelloWord.java，然后回车，你会发现刚刚的文件夹中多了一个HelloWord.class文件，说明编译成功 ：</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b2036e1a2a.png" alt="image-20221013225608893" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>接下来运行程序，在窗口内输入：java HelloWord，注意：此时不需要写.java后缀，然后回车。</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b205128fd2.png" alt="image-20221013230000929" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>出现Hello World!，那么就运行成功了。</li></ul><img src="https://bu.dusays.com/2024/11/30/674b2067ea5fb.png" alt="image-20221013230049829" style="zoom:80%;" /><ul><li>做完这些就可以开始java学习之旅了</li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
